Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝諸位關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向真正的無冕英雄致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是移民計劃失敗的受害者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在火星圈的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新興國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在嚴酷環境下生活的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回那座名為「地球」的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策劃起了規模宏大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特司令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源於你無能至極的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八魔人名聲掃地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為機師確實出色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作為指揮官又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許再發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣作為是XRounder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉 是我的指揮不利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官是我 責任在我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次讓他們滿意就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據報天神號有行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正單艦駛往索倫城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索倫城？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 可能會有麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索倫城公安局發來的入港航道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確認接收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 開始入港程序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入港後 全力配合衛星方面的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全心全意 別讓對方產生不必要的戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船的艦長是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍捕獲了部分維甘軍機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據徹底細緻的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在機體使用的零部件中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了地球圈索倫科技集團獨有的素材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球圈的企業在為維甘做事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以派遣本艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往索倫科技所在的衛星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防打草驚蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣少數親信部隊前往調查最為合適
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我也會隨行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官來天神號上…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要時不惜採取強制手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癌細胞須切除乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 很可能傷及平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你一定會反對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這正是我隨行的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對維甘不能心慈手軟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會利用你的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走你最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 你對維甘的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連戰艦都開來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌啥 你們又不是第一天幹這行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這次對手是軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠錢和威脅很難奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是來調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明還沒有切實證據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理直氣壯一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼按預定計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去會見索倫社負責人 爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艦之長真不好當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最擅長交涉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游刃有餘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不至於 很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一出什麼意外有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只管專心完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米·盧斯上士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明日野司令的AGE1嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼近距離目睹傳說中的機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打掃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 彈射器有點髒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有自動清洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 家裏的玄關要親手清理乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄關？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號如果是家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是玄關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給人感覺就像自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乘員在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 就好像和家人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我算是蕾米的哥哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號所有人裏 中尉是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以無話不說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對長官這樣說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 每次都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 想看看你有沒有空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命可不是自由活動時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回待命室去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道！馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們協助調查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們也希望早日洗清嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免造成不必要的業務損失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次您是一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為調查 其實內容很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只問幾個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實不擅長幹這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一片是擺設嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到找到這兒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們不會輕易收手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏是維甘佔領地球的重要據點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是我們計劃中不可缺少的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現的太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 蜜蕾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到沃爾夫少校信號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現證據！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎·穆萊中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從現在起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在菲利特·明日野中將的指揮下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長外出時 本艦指揮由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行使聯邦軍權限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取設施控制權
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中的機動戰士隊 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動機動戰士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然發現與維甘私下勾結的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的居民區進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會造成很多無辜傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動機動戰士不是唯一的解決辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人徵求你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不殲滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷亡會進一步擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該考慮把犧牲控制在最小限度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不是你說了算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是身為指揮官的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間的遲疑 可能導致無法挽回的惡果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜犧牲市民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會服從這樣的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士隊的指揮由奧布萊特中尉負責
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adele裝備TITUS裝備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是高達的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆那傢伙 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎 走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是被逼的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘威脅我們 迫不得已…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保全索倫城 只能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾絲 上車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我必須去安排工人避難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我去完成自己最後的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子壓根兒沒打算乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經打到這種地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這種情形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸還會說那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打敗維甘 這是不得已？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你說得都對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家誰不難過？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令一定也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 傑哈特和你戰鬥時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不再有迷茫 幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不難過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙終究是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是維甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎她們情況不妙 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不殲滅敵人 傷亡會進一步擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間的遲疑 可能帶來無法挽回的惡果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把坐標發給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用自動駕駛放出AGE2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想傷害你 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 只為保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是決不能拱手讓出這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會耍大牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧死不肯交出情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 善後已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認維甘男子死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 物證全部銷毀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在小黑屋裏關一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有東西想給他看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出去感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是無法執行那種命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這麼當兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為男人也不光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是坐上了高達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後只能在戰鬥中尋求答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒空停下腳步煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該超越的既不是老爸也不是別的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:23:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與戰友的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此的思念和相互吸引的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次將他們帶往激烈的戰爭漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運 成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adele是以高達為基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計的量產型機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它取代Genoace
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為聯邦軍主要戰鬥力來源
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為基礎設計來自高達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以換裝TITUS等各式裝備

